### Architecture decisions in the inference layer

| Decision | Rationale |
|---|---|
| **Single base model + adapter swap** | Minimizes VRAM usage; only 1 base model loaded |
| **Thread lock on generation** | Prevents concurrent adapter swaps mid-generation |
| **SSE streaming** | Standard for LLM streaming; works with web/mobile clients |
| **SQLite audit log** | Zero-dependency, file-based, sufficient for POC |
| **Demo mode auth** | Allows running without API keys for development/demo |
| **Canary by random roll** | Simple, stateless traffic splitting |
| **RAG fallback** | If RAG fails, falls back to direct generation |
| **Citations in SSE** | Sent before tokens so UI can display sources while streaming |
| **Tenant isolation validation** | Explicit check that retrieved chunks belong to correct tenant |

